<p><b>What is the difference between Hatha Yoga Pradipika and Gheranda Samhita?</b> In Hathayoga Pradipika 15 Asanas has been described in detail whereas in Gheranda samhitha 32 Asanas has been described. Regarding the most important asanas both texts have given the same names. The order in which asanas are arranged is also different in these traditional texts.</p>
