<p><b>What is Chitta Vritti?</b> The “Chitta Vrittis”, or the fluctuating states of the mind, are: correct perception, delusion, imagination, deep sleep, and memory. “Nirodha” is the cessation of all of these fluctuations. This doesn't necessarily mean that you no longer think or see with your mind.</p>
